<body>
  <main>
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

    <p>
      Keychrome® ("we", "our", or "us") is committed to protecting your
      personal data in compliance with applicable laws, including the
      General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and Thailand’s Personal
      Data Protection Act (PDPA).
    </p>

    <h5>1. Information We Collect</h5>
    <ul>
      <li>Identity Data: Name, username</li>
      <li>Contact Data: Email address, phone number, address</li>
      <li>
        Transaction Data: Purchase history and payment details
        (processed securely via third parties)
      </li>
      <li>Technical Data: IP address, browser type, device info</li>
      <li>Usage Data: Website interactions and behavior</li>
    </ul>

    <h5>2. Legal Basis for Processing (GDPR)</h5>
    <ul>
      <li>Consent: For marketing communications</li>
      <li>Contract: To fulfill orders and services</li>
      <li>Legal Obligation: Compliance with laws</li>
      <li>Legitimate Interest: Improve services and prevent fraud</li>
    </ul>

    <h5>3. Purpose of Data Usage</h5>
    <ul>
      <li>Order processing and delivery</li>
      <li>Customer support</li>
      <li>Marketing (with consent)</li>
      <li>Security and fraud prevention</li>
    </ul>

    <h5>4. Data Sharing</h5>
    <p>We may share your data with:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Payment processors</li>
      <li>Logistics and shipping providers</li>
      <li>IT and analytics service providers</li>
    </ul>

    <h5>5. International Transfers</h5>
    <p>
      Your data may be transferred outside your country with appropriate
      safeguards (e.g., Standard Contractual Clauses).
    </p>

    <h5>6. Data Retention</h5>
    <p>
      We retain data only as long as necessary for legal and business
      purposes.
    </p>

    <h5>7. Your Rights (GDPR & PDPA)</h5>
    <ul>
      <li>Access your personal data</li>
      <li>Request correction or deletion</li>
      <li>Withdraw consent</li>
      <li>Object to processing</li>
      <li>Data portability</li>
      <li>Lodge complaints with regulatory authorities</li>
    </ul>

    <h5>8. Cookies</h5>
    <p>We use cookies to enhance user experience and analyze traffic.</p>

    <h5>9. Data Security</h5>
    <p>
      We implement technical and organizational measures to protect your
      data.
    </p>

    <h5>10. Contact</h5>
    <p>Email: <a href="mailto:support@keychrome.com">Send an email</a></p>

    <h5>11. Updates</h5>
    <p>We may update this policy periodically.</p>
  </main>
</body>
